    <item>
      <title>巴拉圭着眼于下半年进一步实现债务去美元化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/paraguay-eyes-window-to-further-de-dollarize-debt-in-second-half</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴拉圭财政部长卡洛斯·费尔南德斯表示，如果能够以优惠的利率进行的话，巴拉圭可能会在今年下半年将部分美元债务换成期限较长的本币债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/paraguay-eyes-window-to-further-de-dollarize-debt-in-second-half</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 21:03:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>EyeCare Partners 即将达成债务交换和新融资协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/eyecare-partners-nears-deal-for-debt-exchange-new-financing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，EyeCare Partners LLC 即将达成一项协议，该协议将削减其债务负担，同时还将从一组债权人处获得新资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/eyecare-partners-nears-deal-for-debt-exchange-new-financing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 21:01:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Synovus Trust 的摩根财报对 Netflix 的收益“大吃一惊”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-18/synovus-trust-s-morgan-blown-away-by-netflix-earnings-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Synovus Trust 高级投资组合经理 Daniel Morgan 在彭博电视上对 Netflix 第一季度收益和用户增长做出了反应。 Netflix 在 2024 年第一季度新增了 933 万客户，几乎是分析师平均预期 484 万的两倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-18/synovus-trust-s-morgan-blown-away-by-netflix-earnings-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 20:54:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织表示，一些对冲基金在债券市场上规模太大而不能倒闭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/huge-bond-wagers-make-some-hedge-funds-too-big-to-fail-imf-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织表示，一小部分基金在国债市场积累了如此大的空头押注，以至于在压力时期可能会破坏更广泛的金融体系的稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/huge-bond-wagers-make-some-hedge-funds-too-big-to-fail-imf-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 17:57:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
